drm/i915/guc: Remove GuC stage descriptor, add LRC descriptor

Remove old GuC stage descriptor, add LRC descriptor which will be used
by the new GuC interface implemented in this patch series.

v2:
 (John Harrison)
  - s/lrc/LRC/g

